Global Stomach Forceps Market Insights
Stomach Forceps Market size was valued at USD 1.2 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 2.1 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 8.0% from 2024 to 2030.

Stomach Forceps Market Overview
The global stomach forceps market is valued at approximately USD 500 million in 2024 and is projected to grow steadily at a compound annual growth rate (CAGR) of 4.5% from 2024 to 2030. The growth is driven by the increasing demand for advanced surgical tools, coupled with rising incidences of gastrointestinal disorders. Stomach forceps are widely used in endoscopic procedures and surgeries, contributing significantly to the market expansion. The demand for minimally invasive surgeries is a key factor propelling market growth, especially in the developing regions where healthcare infrastructure is improving.

